title: New Earth Resources Comments on U.S. Proclamation to Strengthen Critical Minerals Supply Chains
description: Vancouver, British Columbia, Jan. 22, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- NEW EARTH RESOURCES CORP. (CSE: EATH) (“New Earth” or the “Company”) has welcomed President Trump's January 14, 2026, U.S. Presidential Proclamation issued under Section 232 of the Trade Expansion Act of 1962, which addresses imports of processed critical minerals and derivative products into the United States.
